---
title: Beef Rump & Thyme Sauce with Potato Mash & Roast Veggie Toss
description: Get creative on this family classic with our buttery garlic and thyme sauce - the seared beef rump’s new best friend. Stacked with colourful roasted veggies and a smooth potato mash, it’s bound to beat all your dinnertime cravings.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thyme-beef-rump-87930213.jpg
